The options of your server explained
In this guide, we'll describe to you all the available options for your server.

Please note:

Every change on the options page requires your server to be restarted to take effect.
Some options are available for all software types, and some others are only available to a specific type of software.
Plugins can overwrite the behavior of some options. If something does not work as intended, check your plugins first.
General options:
Slots
The slots define how many players can play on your server at the same time. This setting does not affect the performance of your server.

Gamemode
