Install plugins (Minecraft: Java Edition)
Plugins allow you to enhance your Minecraft gameplay with new features, commands, and functionalities. In this article, we will explain how to easily install plugins on your Aternos Minecraft: Java Edition server.

Install a supported server software for plugins
You have to install a server software that allows the use of plugins. Currently available on Aternos are:

PaperMC (recommended): https://aternos.org/software/papermc/
Purpur: https://aternos.org/software/purpur/
Spigot: https://aternos.org/software/spigot/
