Install modpacks (Minecraft: Java Edition)
Aternos offers a wide range of modpacks for Minecraft Java Edition published on modded launchers like CurseForge, Modrinth, ATLauncher and the FTB App. In this article, we will show you how to install a modpack on your server and your computer.

Install the modpack on your server
You can install supported modpacks directly in the software section of your Aternos server. Please note that modpacks are full modded experiences. You can only use one modpack at a time and can't change or add individual mods or configurations.  If you want to build your own modpack with custom mods and configs, follow this guide instead: Install Mods

